post_text: The virtual classrooms have been readied, the log in information sent. Meet-and-greets happened throughout the week, and devices and supplies were picked up (first round). Teachers have completed an entire "season of learning," and the Return 2 Learn plan is set. Today we chose a one word intention to focus on throughout the year. And we were reminded that in times of change, the most powerful thing we can do is access our imagination. The future happens now! And one thing is for certain - we can't wait to see our students! See you all Monday, San Gabriel! #sangabrielexperience

So proud of our Roosevelt Music Immersion Experience (MIE) program, and of our students and our staff. On Thursday, December 5th, Roosevelt received the School Board Association 🔔 Golden Bell Award for Closing the Opportunity Gap through LCAP Implementation.
Thank you Samantha Theisen for developing our 🎶 ideas into a dynamic program that allow our students to explore music and have choice. Thank you to our San Gabriel Board of Education for supporting our MIE program and Roosevelt. And to our core teachers and staff, and our MIE staff, thank you for working together to make our Roosvelt family shine and for supporting each other, our students, and their families!♥️
#RooseveltRocks#RooseveltBears
#RooseveltMIE#SGUSD

post_text: Go Eagles!
shared_text:
Gabrielino Eagle Marching Regiment is at Canyon Springs High School 23100 Cougar Canyon Rd, Moreno Valley, Ca 92557.
October 6, 2019 at 12:44 PM · Moreno Valley, CA ·

First comp of the season was a success! Brought home some hardware from the Canyon Springs Field Tournament yesterday in Moreno Valley. 3rd places for band and color guard (out of 5), but the definite highlight of the night was percussion bringing home 3rd place overall! This is not an easy feat to accomplish for a 1A band, but they beat out all other schools in 1A, 2A, 3A, and 4A! First three places were separated by only four points, and the top two bands were 6A! Definitely a huge accomplishment and a great start to the season. See you all at our next comp at Baldwin Park HS on 10/19! 🎶❤️🥁 @ Canyon Springs High School 23100 Cougar Canyon Rd, Moreno Valley, Ca 92557
